
=== configure terminal ===
configure terminal
gpon-olt-Estero-Medio(config)#

=== show alarm ? ===
show alarm 
  configuration  Specify alarm or event configuration.
  id             alarm id
  code           alarm code
  level          alarm level
  summary        show total alarm number
  oamlog         Specify onu oam log.
  information    Specify alarm or event information.
gpon-olt-Estero-Medio(config)# show alarm 
% Command incomplete.
gpon-olt-Estero-Medio(config)#

=== show alarm summary ===
show alarm summary

alarm summary: 0
